{lang-eng}Rakshana ounnatyamu rakshakude
Thelupunu parvatha shikharashrenulavaleney
Nishchala mainadi{/lang-eng}

{lang-hin}महान उद्धार जो है, प्रगट किया प्रभु ने,
पर्वत की चोटी से ऊँचा महान,
और स्थिर भी किया है{/lang-hin}

{lang-eng}Malina vastramu valene nindiyuntimi nindalatho
Thandri maadirigaa mamu vedakivachchi vintaga
Mammu rakshinchenu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Aranya pradeshamulo paadaina yedaarilo
Kanugonenu, paraamarshinchen kanupaapa
Vale gaachen{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Yaakobuvale nuntimi Ishraayeluga maarchenu
Thana swaastyamugaa, thana bhaagamugaa
Thana janamugaa naitimi{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Parvathamulanu shrujinchen shrestamainavi
Nichen Abrahaam Moshe Eliya Yesu ekkiri
Shikharamulanu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Pakshiraaju vale prabhuvu rekkalatho mamu
Moyun alasataleka, mamu pattukoni
Aakasamuna nadupunu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Yesuni satyamulu parvatha shikharamulu
Paripoornamagu prabhu rakshananu
Parikimpa jeyunu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Yeshayaa pravachanamulu rakshana
Vivaramulu shikhara shreni yanubhavamulu
Shikharamu pai pondumu{/lang-eng}

